Euro Needs Political Union, Schaeuble Tells Die Welt

-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 
2011-10-01T12:49:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-01/euro-needs-political-union-schaeuble-tells-die-welt.html
Europe  must push political
integration to end the debt crisis, creating a new form of
political “governance” between sovereign states that falls
short of setting up a continental “super state,” German
Finance Minister  Wolfgang Schaeuble  said in a guest column in
the Welt-am-Sonntag newspaper.  Without such enhanced political coordination  Germany  will
loose influence in Europe, Schaeuble stated.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Brian Parkin at 
 bparkin@bloomberg.net  